snippet: A Saudi inmate held for 12 years at the U.S. prison at Guantanamo Bay, Cuba, on suspicion of fighting in Afghanistan for al Qaeda has been transferred to Saudi Arabia, the U.S. Defense Department said on Saturday....

headline.print_headline: U.S. Releases Guantanamo Prisoner to Saudi Arabia
headline.main: U.S. Releases Guantanamo Prisoner to Saudi Arabia

lead_paragraph: A Saudi inmate held for 12 years at the U.S. prison at Guantanamo Bay, Cuba, on suspicion of fighting in Afghanistan for al Qaeda has been transferred to Saudi Arabia, the U.S. Defense Department said on Saturday.
